review:
I had consulted Dr. Archi when one of my tooth was broken halfway due to decay. She treated me at her ultra modern Archi Advanced Dental Care centre in Ashok Vihar. The ambience in the clinic was very soothing. My treatment required 5 to 6 sittings spread over 3 weeks. During the entire procedure her office handled appointments and follow up activities to ensure minimum waiting time for me, while Dr. Archi led me through different steps of treatment including Root Canal procedure and building up of broken tooth  with utmost care.

I am delighted with services of ARCHI ADVANCED DENTAL CARE.

Rakesh Kumar Shah, General Manager,
Siora Surgicals Pvt. Ltd.
New Delhi.
